I made this Beef Stroganoff and it came out wonderful. It's going to be a keeper in our house. It was so easy to make and is now one of my go to comfy foods to share with others. 
Of course I had to make it my own, because I am gluten free, dairy free, and sugar free, but it was so easy to convert. This is so key for me to be able to do. 
Thank you for a wonderful tasting recipe! Sorry forgot to take a picture and it was gone so fast didn't get the shot. ;
